column1: 2233|10.33|He looked at his watch: 10.33. He remembered being told
column2: he couldn't recall when or by whom
column3: that it was her practice to take her nightly swim shortly after nine o'clock.

column2:
yesss. RECORDING CURRENT PROGRAM. Have done it!
Aargh. All going mad. Cassette has started rewinding and now stopped and ejected. Why? Shit. Shit. Realize in excitement have sat on remote control.
